# Widget Standards

Widgets should be:

Small

Focused

Reusable

Composable

Testable

---

# Responsibilities

One widget

One responsibility.

Avoid widgets exceeding 250 lines.

---

# Constructors

Prefer required parameters.

Avoid nullable values when unnecessary.

---

# Build Method

Keep build methods concise.

Extract private widgets when complexity grows.

---

# Performance

Use const constructors whenever possible.

Minimize rebuilds.

---

# Cursor Instructions

Always favor composition over large monolithic widgets.